Name: Squirrel Jump
About the game: Play as the Squirrel in this endless running 2D game. Filled with excitement and fun, this game will entertain you a lot. Run, dash, and jump your way through the forest, waterfalls, caves and other challenging terrains! The best endless runner game! Unlock your favorite Squirrel and get ready to run. FEATURE: • Collect dozens of rare and unique Squirrels • Play as every Squirrel you unlock • 2D graphics with many beautiful effects • Easy controller by mouse • Shop system • Easy to learn How To Play : • Hold left mouse button to jump higher • Dodge obstacles & enemies • Collect nuts
